⊗ mgks::genesis "strategic_insight"
∴ Schema for synthesis and launch-path decisions

◈ template strategic_insight {
    required:  thesis         ⟨str⟩
    required:  confidence     ⟨f32: 0.0..1.0⟩
    required:  domain         ⟨Strategic | Temporal | Market⟩

    optional:  constraints    ⟨str⟩
    optional:  owner          ⟨str⟩

    default_tier:    t3
    default_decay:   90d
    default_domain:  Strategic
    agents:          [conductor, closer, mother_ai]
}
